<function>

access:  static public

name: register

param: string, $key

param: object|string, $spec

param: mixed, $config, NULL

return: void

</function>

Registers an object under a unique name.

* Parameters:

 * string //$key//: The name under which to register the object.

 * object|string //$spec//: The registry specification.

 * mixed //$config//: If lazy-loading, use this as the config.

* Returns void